                            <comment id="13882479" author="markrmiller@gmail.com" created="Sun, 26 Jan 2014 23:37:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This looks like it is the write cache. Workaround is to disable the write cache in HdfsDirectoryFactory: solr.hdfs.blockcache.write.enabled=false&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Index is not actually corrupt on disk, you can restart on it fine.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
